modules.description: This module reads and parses DBF files, supporting various database formats like FoxPro, dBASE, and Visual FoxPro. It extracts structured data into typed columns, handling fields such as integers, floats, strings, dates, and memos, along with metadata like file type, record count, and field properties. Use it to load legacy database files into OCaml applications for data migration, analysis, or integration with modern systems.
